## Phase 4 — API & Auth Optimization (Days 7-10)

> [!CAUTION]
> Phase 4 contains the **highest-impact single change** (Task 4.1). It's also the most complex. Test thoroughly.

---

### Task 4.1 — Replace Self-Referential Middleware Auth
**Files:**
- [middleware.ts](file:///c:/VamsiKrishna/Github/Tusker-managment/middleware.ts)
- [auth.ts](file:///c:/VamsiKrishna/Github/Tusker-managment/src/lib/auth.ts)  

**Time:** 1 day · **Risk:** High · **Score Impact:** +15 (API) · **Latency Savings: -280ms per page**

**Problem:** The middleware makes a [fetch()](file:///c:/VamsiKrishna/Github/Tusker-managment/src/components/task/kanban/kanban-card.tsx#55-64) to its own `/api/auth/get-session` on every protected route. This is a full HTTP round-trip through the serverless function cold start path.

**Solution:** Read the session cookie directly in middleware using `better-auth`'s cookie-based session verification:

```typescript
// middleware.ts — New approach
import { NextRequest, NextResponse } from "next/server";

export default async function middleware(request: NextRequest) {
    const { pathname } = request.nextUrl;

    // Public routes
    const publicRoutes = ["/", "/sign-in", "/sign-up", "/verify-email"];
    if (publicRoutes.includes(pathname)) return NextResponse.next();

    if (pathname.startsWith("/w/")) {
        // Read session token directly from cookie (no HTTP round-trip)
        const sessionToken = request.cookies.get("better-auth.session_token")?.value;

        if (!sessionToken) {
            return NextResponse.redirect(new URL("/sign-in", request.url));
        }

        // The actual session validation happens in the server component
        // via requireUser() which is cached per-request
        return NextResponse.next();
    }

    return NextResponse.next();
}
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The session cookie name depends on your `better-auth` configuration. Check [src/lib/auth.ts](file:///c:/VamsiKrishna/Github/Tusker-managment/src/lib/auth.ts) to find the exact cookie name. Common names: `better-auth.session_token`, `__session`, `session`.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] No [fetch()](file:///c:/VamsiKrishna/Github/Tusker-managment/src/components/task/kanban/kanban-card.tsx#55-64) call in middleware
- [ ] Middleware execution time < 5ms (from ~300ms)
- [ ] Protected routes still redirect unauthenticated users
- [ ] Email verification flow still works
- [ ] Session expiry still handled by [requireUser()](file:///c:/VamsiKrishna/Github/Tusker-managment/src/lib/auth/require-user.ts#70-80) in server components

