## Final Verification Checklist

Run this checklist after all 5 phases are complete:

### Frontend (Target: 97/100)
- [ ] First Load JS ≤ 160 kB (from 401 kB)
- [ ] `react-icons` removed from package.json
- [ ] `recharts`, `xlsx-js-style`, `@tiptap/*`, `react-date-range` dynamically imported
- [ ] `KanbanCard` and `KanbanColumn` wrapped in `React.memo`
- [ ] Kanban columns virtualized with `@tanstack/react-virtual`
- [ ] No `console.log` in any component hot path
- [ ] `optimizePackageImports` configured in next.config.ts
- [ ] `serverExternalPackages` configured for server-only libs
- [ ] All Zustand usages use selectors
- [ ] SubTaskSheet lazy-loaded

### API (Target: 98/100)
- [ ] Middleware auth does NOT make `fetch()` calls
- [ ] Kanban initial fetch ≤ 50 per column
- [ ] Context expansion capped at 500 tasks
- [ ] API routes have `Cache-Control` headers
- [ ] No `console.log` in server action hot paths

### Database (Target: 99/100)
- [ ] Prisma query logging disabled in production
- [ ] `subtaskCount` / `completedSubtaskCount` denormalized on Task
- [ ] Connection pooling configured
- [ ] Missing indexes added (DailyReport, Task)
- [ ] No `console.log` in data fetching layer

### Infrastructure (Target: 98/100)
- [ ] SEO metadata is correct (not "Create Next App")
- [ ] Semi-static pages use ISR (`revalidate`)
- [ ] Redis caching on hot metadata queries
- [ ] `serverExternalPackages` prevents server libs in client bundle

